block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: Among Us there is an Imposter!!! After my bookmark I wanted to make a better tutorial. This one is a standing model of the Among Us Character. No scissors, no glue, pure origami. Try it out, I hope you like it. Enjoy!!! Learn how to fold the bookmark here: Moderato Origami - Among Us Character Bookmark by Wilson Lee (Heap Art) (No Glue, No Scissors) https://youtu.be/c4hs_9jXnpk Quickie Origami - Among Us Character Bookmark by Wilson Lee (Heap Art) (No Glue, No Scissors) https://youtu.be/T_8rXFCqC-0 Thanks For Watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
